      "description": "Hey there! You guys, you seriously have to see this car\u2014it is an absolute dream! It\u2019s in total mint condition and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out, and it drives like a cloud. I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking to pass it on to someone who will love it just as much as I have. It\u2019s a total gem and ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
