    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform. The naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 remains mechanically pristine, exhibiting flawless throttle response across the 8,400 RPM sweep thanks to meticulously maintained individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast actuation, paired with a variable M differential lock that ensures surgical power delivery to the rear wheels. The chassis is factory-tight, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and an unblemished carbon fiber roof panel. With zero evidence of rod bearing wear or subframe fatigue, this is an investment-grade specimen offering peak kinematic performance and showroom-floor aesthetics.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
